{"tid":255800,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"救命究竟係我係濕疹定皮膚敏感","createTime":"2017-05-24T05:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T01:00:22.000Z","uid":104477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9aec731afc77d9e7a1ff76e736a2e4246a896f0e","tid":255800,"uid":104477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/245171/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/245171/page/1</a><br />\n事源係咁<br />\n睇醫生又話我係皮膚敏感<br />\n低但我以前都冇試過咁<br />\n話因為花粉症季節<br />\n叫我介口,我已經介哂口同埋食哂醫生俾D藥<br />\n點解仲會係咁生出黎<br />\n床又清潔過一次<br />\n唔夠兩日又開始發作<br />\n手腳位好似俾D蚊針咁,又唔係痕<br />\n但過左一陣會變紅<br />\n屎忽大脾手腳都有<br />\n有朋友話咁係濕疹,但上網睇D圖覺得唔係好似<br />\n點解會咁架究竟點解會咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebc620772cc372a45b0815ec34a651bf06934bf","tid":255800,"uid":34983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"風癩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333b9449a15bbf8bd490b9e7fb109cc4891e033d","tid":255800,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:22:30.000Z","msg":"無圖學人開post"},{"pid":"a2bdbb0b7eea8ec5cdf5aa8027b1a95c298e2f07","tid":255800,"uid":104477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:24:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無圖學人開post</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/55/2016/10/20/8/88855891e3a500030aa60ea17f46b0c6.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F55%2F2016%2F10%2F20%2F8%2F88855891e3a500030aa60ea17f46b0c6.jpg&d=IZWl12S5z6lUnueYSkvqYUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=44872cf1\" target=\"_blank\">http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/55/2016/10/20/8/88855891e3a500030aa60ea17f46b0c6.jpg</a>